comment:
* Class to represent a request based on time range and data origin filters for {@link
 * HealthConnectManager#readRecords(ReadRecordsRequest, Executor, OutcomeReceiver)}
 *
 * @param <T> the type of the Record for the request

methods.name: public TimeRangeFilter getTimeRangeFilter()
methods.comment: Returns time range b/w which the read operation is to be performed

methods.name: public Set<DataOrigin> getDataOrigins()
methods.comment: * Returns the set of {@link DataOrigin data origins} to be read, or empty list for no filter

methods.name: public int getPageSize()
methods.comment: Returns maximum number of records to be returned by the read operation

methods.name: public long getPageToken()
methods.comment: Returns page token to read the current page of the result. -1 if none available

methods.name: public boolean isAscending()
methods.comment: Returns ordering of results to be returned

methods.name: public ReadRecordsRequestParcel toReadRecordsRequestParcel()
methods.comment:
* Returns an object of ReadRecordsRequestParcel to carry read request
     *
     * @hide
